This relief fragment depicts the god #Vishnu holding the #chakra, or wheel, which symbolizes the cycle of creation and destruction. Carved from fine-grained stone typical of the #Bengali region, which allows for the carving of ornate details and precise lines, the image was created to adorn a niche in the walls of a #Hindu temple. ⠀
